46:06.280 --> 46:10.240
All right, enough!
That's... Stand up.

46:12.120 --> 46:15.440
Ash. I know ash.

46:21.720 --> 46:23.880
I have an international reputation.

46:25.920 --> 46:28.559
Do you have
an international reputation?

46:28.560 --> 46:31.760
No, I don't have
an international reputation. No.

46:34.640 --> 46:36.480
