47:12.920 --> 47:14.039
Funny!

47:14.040 --> 47:15.279
Thank you.

47:15.280 --> 47:18.480
Come on. No, you're not
a vegetable. It's your go.

47:20.160 --> 47:23.639
Erm... am I human?

47:23.640 --> 47:24.879
Sometimes.

47:24.880 --> 47:26.239
Can't have sometimes.

47:26.240 --> 47:27.439
It has to be, um...

47:27.440 --> 47:31.039
Yes, you're human.
Yes, I know, OK. And am I a man?

47:31.040 --> 47:32.520
Yep. Tall?

47:34.160 --> 47:35.759
Not as tall as people think.

47:35.760 --> 47:37.439
Hmm. Nice?

47:37.440 --> 47:38.919
Ish.

47:38.920 --> 47:39.999
Clever?

47:40.000 --> 47:41.039
I would say so.

47:41.040 --> 47:42.319
You would.

47:42.320 --> 47:44.159
Hmm, am I important?

47:44.160 --> 47:45.719
To some people.

47:45.720 --> 47:48.399
Do people like me?

47:48.400 --> 47:50.199
Erm, no they don't.

47:50.200 --> 47:53.239
You tend to rub them up
the wrong way.

47:53.240 --> 47:54.839
OK.

47:54.840 --> 47:56.920
Am I the current King of England?

47:59.200 --> 48:00.959
You know we don't have a King.

48:00.960 --> 48:03.119
Don't we? No.

48:03.120 --> 48:05.080
Your go.

48:11.760 --> 48:14.360
I don't mind. Am I a woman?

48:16.400 --> 48:18.440
What?

48:19.440 --> 48:20.679
Yes.

48:20.680 --> 48:23.400
Am I... pretty?

48:24.760 --> 48:26.000
This?

48:27.760 --> 48:30.879
Beauty is a construct based
entirely on childhood impressions,

48:30.880 --> 48:32.639
influences and role models.

48:32.640 --> 48:35.120
Yeah, but am I a pretty lady?

48:37.640 --> 48:41.199
I don't know who you are, I don't
know who you're supposed to be.

48:41.200 --> 48:42.399
You picked the name!

48:42.400 --> 48:44.439
But I picked it at random
from the papers.

48:44.440 --> 48:47.839
You're not really getting the hang
of this game, are you, Sherlock?

48:47.840 --> 48:52.279
So I am human, I'm not as tall
as people think I am. I'm...

48:52.280 --> 48:54.399
I'm nice-ish, clever,

48:54.400 --> 48:55.999
important to some people.

48:56.000 --> 48:58.840
But I tend to rub them up
the wrong way.

49:00.400 --> 49:01.839
Got it.

49:01.840 --> 49:03.559
Go on, then. I'm you, aren't I?

49:03.560 --> 49:04.560
Client!

49:06.520 --> 49:07.839
Hello.

49:07.840 --> 49:10.039
Hello. Come on.

49:10.040 --> 49:12.040
Which one of you is Sherlock Holmes?

49:17.520 --> 49:19.199
I don't... a lot.

49:19.200 --> 49:22.199
I mean, I don't date all that much.

49:22.200 --> 49:27.159
And he seemed nice, you know?

49:27.160 --> 49:30.039
We seemed to automatically connect.

49:30.040 --> 49:31.479
We had one night,

49:31.480 --> 49:35.199
dinner, such interesting
conversation.

49:35.200 --> 49:37.439
It was lovely.

49:37.440 --> 49:38.959
To be honest,

49:38.960 --> 49:41.719
I'd love to have gone further,

49:41.720 --> 49:45.919
but I thought, no, this is special,

49:45.920 --> 49:47.679
let's take it slowly.

49:47.680 --> 49:49.239
Exchanged numbers,

49:49.240 --> 49:51.760
he said he'd get in touch
and then...

49:55.040 --> 50:00.679
Maybe he wasn't quite
as keen as I was,

50:00.680 --> 50:04.199
but I just thought

50:04.200 --> 50:07.480
at least he'd call
to say that we were finished.

50:14.440 --> 50:16.559
I went round there,

50:16.560 --> 50:19.879
to his flat, no trace of him.

50:19.880 --> 50:24.319
Mr.. Holmes, I honestly think

50:24.320 --> 50:28.440
I had dinner with a ghost.

50:32.520 --> 50:34.120
Mr.. Holmes?

50:39.320 --> 50:41.239
With a ghost, Mr.. Holmes!

50:41.240 --> 50:45.720
Boring, boring, boring.
No... fascinating.

50:46.960 --> 50:48.639
John. John! Wake up.

50:48.640 --> 50:52.239
I apologise about my...
You know... Him.

50:52.240 --> 50:53.600
Rude. Rude!

50:55.280 --> 50:57.399
I checked with the landlord

50:57.400 --> 51:00.599
and the man who lived there died.

51:00.600 --> 51:02.479
Heart attack.

51:02.480 --> 51:06.439
And there we are
having dinner one week on.

51:06.440 --> 51:09.879
And I found this thing online,

51:09.880 --> 51:12.359
a sort of chatroom thing,

51:12.360 --> 51:16.599
for girls who think they're dating
men from the spirit world.

51:16.600 --> 51:20.039
Don't worry, I'll find him
in ten minutes.

51:20.040 --> 51:21.319
What's your dog's name?

51:21.320 --> 51:23.959
Yeah, I'm there if you want it...
John, wake up.

51:23.960 --> 51:26.479
Went to... Yeah.

51:26.480 --> 51:28.160
The game is... something.

51:29.160 --> 51:30.239
On?

51:30.240 --> 51:31.879
Yeah, that, that.

51:31.880 --> 51:33.040
OK.

51:42.400 --> 51:44.519
Oh, it's nice.

51:44.520 --> 51:46.240
Nice place.

51:51.320 --> 51:53.439
