56:21.440 --> 56:22.599
Oh.

56:22.600 --> 56:25.719
It was purely physical
between me and Frank.

56:25.720 --> 56:28.079
We couldn't keep
our hands off each other.

56:28.080 --> 56:30.639
I know, there was one night...

56:30.640 --> 56:32.080
Oh, is that Sherlock?

