Is it?

56:33.920 --> 56:35.160
That's Sherlock.

56:40.200 --> 56:41.840
Urgh...

56:55.640 --> 56:57.439
There are going to be others.

56:57.440 --> 57:00.479
Others? VictiMs.., women.

57:00.480 --> 57:02.599
Most ghosts tend to
haunt a single house.

57:02.600 --> 57:05.160
This ghost, however,
is willing to commute. Look.

57:26.680 --> 57:30.079
Hmm... Not you. Not you.

