57:44.320 --> 57:46.719
Not you. Not you.
Not you. Not you. Not you.

57:46.720 --> 57:47.879
Not you, you, you, or you, or you.

57:47.880 --> 57:52.159
Or not you, not you, not you,
not you, not you, not you.

