Not you.

58:01.520 --> 58:03.359
Hi.

58:03.360 --> 58:04.880
Gail.

58:10.200 --> 58:11.720
Charlotte.

58:13.200 --> 58:15.440
Robyn.

58:17.960 --> 58:19.480
Vicky.

58:27.160 --> 58:29.239
How did you meet?

58:29.240 --> 58:31.479
Came up to me in a pub.
