58:31.480 --> 58:33.519
We just got chatting on the bus.

58:33.520 --> 58:34.599
Online.

58:34.600 --> 58:36.599
Name? Told you.

58:36.600 --> 58:38.399
His name. Oscar.

58:38.400 --> 58:40.279
Mike. Terry.

58:40.280 --> 58:42.839
Erm... Love Monkey.

58:42.840 --> 58:44.599
Your place?

58:44.600 --> 58:45.880
His place.

58:47.080 --> 58:48.320
Address?

58:52.520 --> 58:53.719
Nothing happened.

58:53.720 --> 58:56.799
It was just... very romantic.

58:56.800 --> 58:59.519
Four women in four nights.
He must have something special.

58:59.520 --> 59:01.199
He was very charming. He listened.

59:01.200 --> 59:02.359
He was sweet.

59:02.360 --> 59:05.719
He had a lovely... You OK?

