He had a lovely manner.

59:17.600 --> 59:20.639
Different names,
different addresses.

59:20.640 --> 59:21.999
Describe him.

59:22.000 --> 59:23.079
Short blonde hair.

59:23.080 --> 59:24.479
Dark hair. Long.

59:24.480 --> 59:26.119
Ginger. I like gingers.

