James, stop it, right now!

01:15:53.840 --> 01:15:55.559
I will kick this door down!

01:15:55.560 --> 01:15:58.479
Mr.. Holmes, you and
I are similar, I think.

01:15:58.480 --> 01:16:01.279
Yes, I think we are. There's
a proper time to die, isn't there?

01:16:01.280 --> 01:16:02.599
Of course there is.

01:16:02.600 --> 01:16:06.319
And one should embrace it
when it comes.

01:16:06.320 --> 01:16:07.359
Like a soldier.

01:16:07.360 --> 01:16:10.160
