be arresting, Mr.. Holmes.

01:19:42.600 --> 01:19:45.159
Oh, I don't do the arresting,
I just farm that out.

01:19:45.160 --> 01:19:47.359
Sholto, he's the killer, not me.

01:19:47.360 --> 01:19:49.600
I should have killed him quicker.

01:19:52.200 --> 01:19:54.120
I shouldn't have tried to be clever.

01:19:55.480 --> 01:19:57.280
You should have driven faster.

01:20:06.600 --> 01:20:07.920
Right.

01:21:26.520 --> 01:21:28.519
Ladies and gentlemen,
just one last thing

01:21:28.520 --> 01:21:30.559
before the evening begins properly.

01:21:30.560 --> 01:21:34.319
Apologies for earlier,
a crisis arose and was dealt with.

01:21:34.320 --> 01:21:36.319
More importantly, however,

01:21:36.320 --> 01:21:38.199
