01:21:38.200 --> 01:21:39.639
I've never made a vow in my life

01:21:39.640 --> 01:21:41.399
and after tonight
I never will again.

01:21:41.400 --> 01:21:43.599
So, here in front of you all,

01:21:43.600 --> 01:21:45.320
